column5: Is it still a go for the Rags?
Yes, the rags are still a go. I just returned today from the trip and we took the rags both ways! Good luck
Lakes.Area,Should have looked a little further down the page to see your report. Curious as how deep you found them?

Fishing was good! It always is up there. We found them anywhere from 9-17 ft. We would find them everywhere we went but they were not stacked like in previous trips, but we always found fish. When do you go up there?
Be there Friday. Wish I could leave in the morning. Gonna be a long week at work!

brought the houseboat through the RAGS on Friday the 15th. fished it a little too and saw about 4.5 -5 fow in the channel. fishing was real good for us most fish for us were from 14-22 fow. real slow for northerns for us though. maybe a little less in the numbers department but much better in the size department on average. i would say we got as many fish in the slot or over than we got under.
